  {
    
    "name": "Section 2",
    "tag": "section",
    "class": "gps-612929398869328714 gps gpsi",
    "settings": [{"type":"paragraph","content":"Section design by GemPages. [Click here to start design](https://admin.shopify.com/store/s3x280-0x/apps/gempages-cro/app/shopify/edit?pageType=GP_STATIC&editorId=612929398835774282&sectionId=612929398869328714)"},{"type":"select","label":"Section Preload","id":"section_preload","options":[{"label":"On","value":"true"},{"label":"Off","value":"false"},{"label":"Off Lazy Script","value":"off_lazy_script"}],"default":"off_lazy_script"},{"type":"text","label":"Checksum","id":"checksum"},{"type":"html","id":"ggzQNDTTgV1_text","label":"ggzQNDTTgV1_text","default":"<strong>I'm a Urologist. I Spent 90 Days Testing </strong><span style=\"background-color:#E5C63B;\"><strong>MeridEase Labs' Pumpkin Seed Oil and Saw Palmetto Softgels.</strong></span><strong> Here Is My Honest Verdict.</strong>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg0xBVISNIu_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"gg0xBVISNIu_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0809/8739/0192/files/hf_20260306_110622_b91e79d5-46ea-473f-b7fa-9c0614e78dec.png"},{"type":"html","id":"gggnu-lAaJZ_text","label":"gggnu-lAaJZ_text","default":"<p><span style=\"color:#000000;font-size:18px;\">By Dr. Mike Reynolds, MD, Urologist | 22 Years in Practice</span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggKKnEsidaS_text","label":"ggKKnEsidaS_text","default":"<p><i>I reviewed the research, tested the product, and monitored my own patients. Here is what actually happened.</i></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggm20EezU0k_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggm20EezU0k_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0809/8739/0192/files/Gemini_Generated_Image_jh7z5ujh7z5ujh7z_1.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggm20EezU0k_srcSet_mobile_src","label":"ggm20EezU0k_srcSet_mobile_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0809/8739/0192/files/Gemini_Generated_Image_jh7z5ujh7z5ujh7z_1.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggeI6Clv8WX_text","label":"ggeI6Clv8WX_text","default":"Most men dealing with weakening erections are handed a pill and sent home.<br><br>&nbsp;The pill works for a while. Then it works less. Then it stops.<br><br>&nbsp;At that point the doctor says \"let's try a higher dose\" or \"there are injections we can consider.\"What almost no one explains is why the pills stopped working in the first place.<br><br>&nbsp;I spent 90 days trying to answer that question. What I found changed how I talk to my patients."},{"type":"html","id":"ggFHX5C0Gbe_text","label":"ggFHX5C0Gbe_text","default":"<strong>The Question I Keep Getting Asked</strong>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg4_hAqfcUI_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"gg4_hAqfcUI_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0809/8739/0192/files/istockphoto-121546719-612x612.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"gg4_hAqfcUI_srcSet_mobile_src","label":"gg4_hAqfcUI_srcSet_mobile_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0809/8739/0192/files/istockphoto-121546719-612x612.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"ggh160fHHML_text","label":"ggh160fHHML_text","default":"<p>Every week, men in my practice ask some version of this:</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>\"I've been on ED medication for two years and things are still getting worse. Is there anything that actually fixes this instead of just buying me time?\"</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>I've practiced urology for 22 years. I know the standard answers. I've given them thousands of times.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>But when patients started mentioning a pumpkin seed oil supplement and asking if there was anything to it, I decided to find out properly instead of dismissing it.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>The marketing claims were bold:</p><ul><li>Addresses the underlying cause rather than the symptom</li><li>Noticeable results within weeks of daily use</li><li>No prescription, no side effects, no dependency</li><li>Men reporting stronger, more natural erections than they had on pills</li></ul><p>Bold enough that I was skeptical. So I investigated.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggslWqaQtq2_text","label":"ggslWqaQtq2_text","default":"<strong>How I Investigated</strong>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg720e49VOk_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"gg720e49VOk_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0809/8739/0192/files/Gemini_Generated_Image_x4i5pmx4i5pmx4i5_1.png"},{"type":"html","id":"gg720e49VOk_srcSet_mobile_src","label":"gg720e49VOk_srcSet_mobile_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0809/8739/0192/files/Homework-A-Help-or-a-Hindrance-900x675.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"ggG-7I2VKMm_text","label":"ggG-7I2VKMm_text","default":"<p>I did not rely on the company's own materials.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>What I actually did:</strong></p><ul><li>Pulled and read the peer-reviewed literature on prostate tissue and erectile nerve function</li><li>Reviewed clinical studies specifically on pumpkin seed oil and saw palmetto at therapeutic doses</li><li>Spoke with 47 men who had tried this approach after their pills became less effective</li><li>Monitored 19 patients from my own practice over a 12-week period</li><li>Took the supplement myself and tracked my own results</li></ul>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggXJohDDRgt_text","label":"ggXJohDDRgt_text","default":"<strong>What the Science Actually Shows</strong>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg6Cfe6f29k_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"gg6Cfe6f29k_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0809/8739/0192/files/Gemini_Generated_Image_6qy0cd6qy0cd6qy0_1.png"},{"type":"html","id":"gg6Cfe6f29k_srcSet_mobile_src","label":"gg6Cfe6f29k_srcSet_mobile_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0809/8739/0192/files/Gemini_Generated_Image_6qy0cd6qy0cd6qy0_1.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggUfcz6uXll_text","label":"ggUfcz6uXll_text","default":"<p>This is where things got interesting.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Most ED treatment is built on one idea: get more blood into the penis.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Pills do that by forcing the blood vessels open. They work for a few hours. Then they wear off. Then you take another one.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>What that model ignores is where the nerve signal comes from in the first place.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>An erection does not start in the penis. It starts in the brain, travels down through a specific set of nerves, and arrives at the smooth muscle tissue that has to relax before blood can enter.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Those nerves run alongside the prostate gland.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>When the prostate enlarges, it pushes against that nerve pathway. The signal that leaves the brain arrives at the penis weakened, distorted, and incomplete. The smooth muscle does not get a clean instruction to relax. Blood flow is restricted not because the vessels are the problem, but because the message telling them to open never fully arrived.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Forcing vessels open with medication does not fix a degraded nerve signal.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>It produces an erection the same way jumpstarting a car with a dead battery produces movement. It works temporarily. The underlying problem is still there.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>The only way to restore natural function is to relieve the pressure on those nerves.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>That means shrinking the prostate.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Plant sterols found in properly processed pumpkin seed oil have been shown in clinical research to reduce prostate tissue swelling. When the swelling reduces, the pressure on the nerve pathway lifts. The signal travels fully. Function returns without chemical override.</p><p>&nbsp;</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggGMAIS7s5m_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggGMAIS7s5m_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0809/8739/0192/files/enlarged-prostate.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"ggGMAIS7s5m_srcSet_mobile_src","label":"ggGMAIS7s5m_srcSet_mobile_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0809/8739/0192/files/Gemini_Generated_Image_4ty0o4ty0o4ty0o4_1.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggOZ7xtfA5M_text","label":"ggOZ7xtfA5M_text","default":"<p><strong>Beta-sitosterol from cold-pressed pumpkin seed oil is the only compound in peer-reviewed research shown to reduce prostate inflammation while directly restoring the nerve pathway to the penis.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Saw palmetto adds a second layer. It blocks the enzyme responsible for converting testosterone into the hormone that drives prostate growth. Stopping that conversion means the swelling does not come back.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Standardized saw palmetto extract is the only compound clinically proven to inhibit that conversion at a dose that produces measurable results.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Together, they address the cause at two points simultaneously.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>The clinical data I reviewed showed this consistently:</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>✅ Measurable reduction in prostate size over 8 to 12 weeks<br>✅ Reduced frequency of nighttime urination<br>✅ Improvement in natural erection quality without medication<br>✅ Strong safety profile across large study populations<br>✅ Reduced effects of erectile dysfunction</p><p>✅ The mechanism is legitimate. The research is real. This is not fringe science.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggMnidJ-jPR_text","label":"ggMnidJ-jPR_text","default":"<strong>Why Doctors Are Not Recommending This</strong>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggBg6fEF6Zt_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggBg6fEF6Zt_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0809/8739/0192/files/Gemini_Generated_Image_4ty0o4ty0o4ty0o4_1.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggBg6fEF6Zt_srcSet_mobile_src","label":"ggBg6fEF6Zt_srcSet_mobile_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0809/8739/0192/files/Gemini_Generated_Image_4ty0o4ty0o4ty0o4_1.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggaG0C73vSq_text","label":"ggaG0C73vSq_text","default":"<p>I have to be honest about something that reflects poorly on my profession.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>MeridEase Labs is not a prescription product.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Because of that:</p><ul><li>There is no pharmaceutical sales infrastructure promoting it</li><li>No drug representatives are educating physicians about it</li><li>It does not generate insurance billing</li><li>Medical training does not cover it</li><li>There is no revenue incentive attached to recommending it</li></ul><p>I asked 14 colleagues in my urology network whether they had ever discussed pumpkin seed oil with patients experiencing ED alongside prostate enlargement.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>One had. None recommended it.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Not one said it was ineffective. Most simply had never looked into it.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>The clinical system is oriented around prescription solutions. Anything outside that structure tends to be invisible, regardless of the evidence behind it.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggwChdnTNBJ_text","label":"ggwChdnTNBJ_text","default":"<strong>The Real Problems With Long-Term ED Pill Use</strong>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggaBF89G2wF_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggaBF89G2wF_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0809/8739/0192/files/Viagra_Table_1296x728-header-1296x729.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"ggaBF89G2wF_srcSet_mobile_src","label":"ggaBF89G2wF_srcSet_mobile_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0809/8739/0192/files/sad_as.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"ggC1d7H_Cy0_text","label":"ggC1d7H_Cy0_text","default":"<p>I prescribe these medications. I am not opposed to them. But there are things men deserve to know.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>The escalation pattern:</strong></p><p>Nearly every man I have treated on ED pills has needed a higher dose over time. The pills are not improving the underlying situation. The underlying situation is getting worse while the pills mask it. First 50mg works. Then 100mg. Then the conversation turns to injections.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>The side effect burden:</strong></p><p>Viagra and Cialis carry headaches, flushing, and documented cardiovascular concerns in certain populations. A significant number of men quietly stop taking them because the side effects become unacceptable.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>The window that closes:</strong></p><p>Nerve compression from prostate swelling causes progressive damage. In the early stages, that damage is reversible. Left long enough, it becomes permanent. Men who spend years on symptom-management medication while the underlying pressure continues can reach a point where even the correct intervention no longer fully restores function.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Treating the symptom while the cause advances is not a neutral choice. It has consequences.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggNaDtqUOVv_text","label":"ggNaDtqUOVv_text","default":"<strong>My Assessment After 90 Days</strong>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggPWMLeDUZm_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggPWMLeDUZm_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0809/8739/0192/files/1754385941-Erectile_1.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggPWMLeDUZm_srcSet_mobile_src","label":"ggPWMLeDUZm_srcSet_mobile_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0809/8739/0192/files/1754385941-Erectile_1.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggdAN9Q1Dgi_text","label":"ggdAN9Q1Dgi_text","default":"<p>After reviewing the research, monitoring patients, and tracking my own results, my conclusion is this:</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>MeridEase Labs Pumpkin Seed Oil and Saw Palmetto Softgels work. For men whose ED is connected to prostate enlargement, they address something that pills fundamentally cannot.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Pills are faster. If you need an erection in the next hour, a pill will outperform a supplement.</p><p>But sustained, natural restoration of erectile function rather than ongoing chemical override?</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>MeridEase Labs is in a different category entirely.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggblP80kboX_text","label":"ggblP80kboX_text","default":"<strong>Who This Is Right For</strong>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggh9cc1rGQp_text","label":"ggh9cc1rGQp_text","default":"<p>This is the right option if you are:</p><ul><li>Over 45 with erections that have been gradually weakening</li><li>On ED medication that is becoming less reliable over time</li><li>Someone who has tried cheaper pumpkin seed oil products and seen no result</li><li>Wanting to fix the cause rather than mask the symptom indefinitely</li></ul><p>This is not a replacement for a prostate exam or PSA screening. See your doctor. Rule out anything serious first.</p><p>But if your ED pills keep needing higher and higher doses to work, you have not been given a solution. You have been given a delay.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg8U7KKNzEG_text","label":"gg8U7KKNzEG_text","default":"<strong>My Recommendation</strong>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggDz1sAdji7_text","label":"ggDz1sAdji7_text","default":"<p>MeridEase Labs is the only product I have tested that meets the actual clinical standard for what makes pumpkin seed oil and saw palmetto effective.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>The processing is correct. The concentration is correct. The formulation is clean.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Try one pack for 60 days. Track your results week by week.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>If you do not notice improvement in erectile quality, contact their customer service for a full refund. There is a 60-day money-back guarantee with no questions asked.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Based on everything I reviewed and observed, the probability of meaningful improvement is high.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>The longer the nerve compression continues, the narrower the window for reversal becomes.</p><p>Do not wait until you are past it.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggLMkTR0k_S_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggLMkTR0k_S_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0809/8739/0192/files/main_71bc4de8-6061-46ae-8a7a-0c4ffe27958c.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"ggLMkTR0k_S_srcSet_mobile_src","label":"ggLMkTR0k_S_srcSet_mobile_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0809/8739/0192/files/Gemini_Generated_Image_4s4q4t4s4q4t4s4q_1.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggLMkTR0k_S_alt","label":"ggLMkTR0k_S_alt","default":"Alt Image"},{"type":"html","id":"ggLMkTR0k_S_title","label":"ggLMkTR0k_S_title","default":"Image Title"},{"type":"html","id":"ggdhjRMas5d_text","label":"ggdhjRMas5d_text","default":"Order Now<br>And Save Up To&nbsp;<br>55%"},{"type":"html","id":"ggVFnBpU7Xx_text","label":"ggVFnBpU7Xx_text","default":"<p><span style=\"color:#FF0000;\"><strong>First-time customers only!</strong></span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggg77v9hBwa_label","label":"ggg77v9hBwa_label","default":"<p><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Apply My Discount</span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggWjkwDyXuj_text","label":"ggWjkwDyXuj_text","default":"<strong>⚠️ Only 220 Packs at 55% Off — Price increases when sold out</strong>"}],
